data.description: **UNDER CONTRACT - ACCEPTING BACK-UP OFFERS. This attractive Craftsman style home was built in 2007.  This home features 10 foot high ceilings with crown molding, 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, large light bright & airy family room with wood burning fireplace, formal dining room, kitchen with breakfast bar, plus breakfast table area, granite countertops with stainless appliances. 2 car attached garage with attic storage. This is a split bedroom plan with a large luxurious master suite. Outside has rocking chair front porch and large rear patio. 5.73 acres on corner lot on paved road.
